flowchart TD
    START[Agent Installed] --> ENROLL[Admin creates host + enrollment token]
    ENROLL --> REG[POST /agent/register with enroll_token]
    REG --> VALID{Token valid?}
    VALID -->|No| REJECT[400 Invalid/Expired]
    VALID -->|Yes| KEY[Generate sk_live_* API key]
    KEY --> STORE[Store api_key_hash + mark token used]
    STORE --> RETURN[Return API key to agent]

    RETURN --> LOOP[Agent Loop]
    LOOP --> HB[POST /heartbeat every 30s]
    LOOP --> EVT[POST /events batch]
    LOOP --> MET[POST /metrics batch]

    HB --> INTEGRITY{Hash changed?}
    INTEGRITY -->|Yes| ALERT[Tamper Alert]
    INTEGRITY -->|No| ONLINE[Update last_seen]

    EVT --> SIGN{Signing enabled?}
    SIGN -->|Yes| VERIFY[HMAC + nonce check]
    SIGN -->|No| INGEST[Pipeline ingest]
    VERIFY --> INGEST

    LOOP --> ROTATE[POST /rotate-key optional]
    ROTATE --> NEWKEY[New key, old revoked]
